---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="DIM Model" description="The DROG DIM categorizes interventions into six generations based on paradigm shifts in counter-disinformation">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Framework</span>
      <h1>Disinformation Intervention Model</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Disinformation adapts. Consequences evolve. Paradigms shift. Next-generation interventions emerge.</p>
      <a href="/drog-manifesto-2026.pdf" target="_blank" class="manifesto-btn">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/>
          <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/>
          <line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12" y2="12"/>
          <line x1="9" y1="15" x2="12" y2="18"/>
          <line x1="15" y1="15" x2="12" y2="18"/>
        </svg>
        Read the 2026 Manifesto
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Immersive Timeline Section -->
  <section class="immersive-timeline">
    <div class="timeline-intro">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="section-label">The Journey</span>
        <h2>The Decade of Disinformation</h2>
        <p>Scroll through the events that shaped our understanding of information warfare  - and the interventions that emerged in response.</p>
        <div class="scroll-indicator">
          <span>Scroll to explore</span>
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 5v14M5 12l7 7 7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-track">
      <div class="timeline-line"></div>

      <!-- 2014 -->
      <div class="timeline-entry" data-year="2014" data-gen="1">
        <div class="entry-marker">
          <span class="marker-year">2014</span>
          <div class="marker-dot"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="entry-card">
          <div class="card-header header-blue">
            <div class="header-icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                <path d="M2 12h20M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="gen-badge">GEN 1 Emerges</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>The Awakening</h3>
            <div class="event-list">
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot blue"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>Crimea & Hybrid Warfare</strong>
                  <p>Russia's annexation combined military action with sophisticated information operations. The West had no playbook.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot green"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>ISIS Online Recruitment</strong>
                  <p>Terrorist organizations mastered social media for radicalization and recruitment.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot purple"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>MH17 Shootdown</strong>
                  <p>Competing narratives emerged instantly. Truth became a battlefield.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="intervention-response">
              <div class="response-label">The Response</div>
              <div class="response-content">
                <strong>Strategic Communication</strong>
                <p>If adversaries spread propaganda, counter with truth. Governments established StratCom units and funded independent journalism.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2016 -->
      <div class="timeline-entry" data-year="2016" data-gen="2">
        <div class="entry-marker">
          <span class="marker-year">2016</span>
          <div class="marker-dot"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="entry-card">
          <div class="card-header header-orange">
            <div class="header-icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z"/>
                <line x1="4" y1="22" x2="4" y2="15"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="gen-badge">GEN 2 Emerges</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>The Election Shock</h3>
            <div class="event-list">
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot orange"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>US Election Interference</strong>
                  <p>Russian troll farms, leaked emails, and viral misinformation. "Fake news" entered the mainstream vocabulary.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="intervention-response">
              <div class="response-label">The Response</div>
              <div class="response-content">
                <strong>Debunking & Fact-Checking</strong>
                <p>Verify claims, label them true or false, trust people will update their beliefs. Platforms partnered with fact-checkers at scale.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2018 -->
      <div class="timeline-entry" data-year="2018" data-gen="3">
        <div class="entry-marker">
          <span class="marker-year">2018</span>
          <div class="marker-dot"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="entry-card">
          <div class="card-header header-purple">
            <div class="header-icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="gen-badge">GEN 3 Emerges</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>The Data Scandal</h3>
            <div class="event-list">
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot purple"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>Cambridge Analytica</strong>
                  <p>Psychological profiling meets political manipulation. The scale of data exploitation was revealed.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="intervention-response">
              <div class="response-label">The Response</div>
              <div class="response-content">
                <strong>Prebunking & Inoculation</strong>
                <p>Instead of correcting falsehoods, teach people to recognize manipulation techniques. Games like Bad News were born.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="drog-highlight">
              <span class="drog-badge">DROG Creates Bad News</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2020 -->
      <div class="timeline-entry" data-year="2020" data-gen="4">
        <div class="entry-marker">
          <span class="marker-year">2020</span>
          <div class="marker-dot"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="entry-card">
          <div class="card-header header-green">
            <div class="header-icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="gen-badge">GEN 4 Emerges</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>The Infodemic</h3>
            <div class="event-list">
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot green"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>COVID-19 Infodemic</strong>
                  <p>Misinformation became a public health crisis. Anti-vax content, miracle cures, and conspiracy theories spread faster than the virus.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="intervention-response">
              <div class="response-label">The Response</div>
              <div class="response-content">
                <strong>Platform Moderation</strong>
                <p>Deplatform, derank, demonetize. The EU's Digital Services Act emerged. Content moderation became serious business.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="drog-highlight">
              <span class="drog-badge">DROG Launches Go Viral!</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2021 -->
      <div class="timeline-entry" data-year="2021">
        <div class="entry-marker">
          <span class="marker-year">2021</span>
          <div class="marker-dot"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="entry-card">
          <div class="card-header header-red">
            <div class="header-icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M3 21h18M5 21V7l8-4 8 4v14M9 21v-6h6v6"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="gen-badge">Moderation Tested</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>The Insurrection</h3>
            <div class="event-list">
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot red"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>January 6th Capitol Attack</strong>
                  <p>Online conspiracy theories manifested as real-world violence. The stakes of disinformation became undeniable.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="intervention-response">
              <div class="response-label">The Lesson</div>
              <div class="response-content">
                <strong>Moderation Has Limits</strong>
                <p>Deplatforming came too late. Users migrated to alternative platforms. The fundamental question emerged: who decides what's true?</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2022 -->
      <div class="timeline-entry" data-year="2022" data-gen="5">
        <div class="entry-marker">
          <span class="marker-year">2022</span>
          <div class="marker-dot"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="entry-card">
          <div class="card-header header-blue">
            <div class="header-icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
                <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
                <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="gen-badge">GEN 5 Emerges</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>The Platform Shift</h3>
            <div class="event-list">
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot orange"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>Ukraine War Disinformation</strong>
                  <p>Real-time information warfare. Competing narratives from day one. OSINT communities emerged as truth-seekers.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot blue"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>Musk Acquires Twitter</strong>
                  <p>A philosophical shift in platform governance. Content moderation policies thrown into chaos.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="intervention-response">
              <div class="response-label">The Response</div>
              <div class="response-content">
                <strong>Interaction & Deliberation</strong>
                <p>Focus shifts from content to connection. Deep canvassing, street epistemology. People change minds through conversation.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2023 -->
      <div class="timeline-entry" data-year="2023">
        <div class="entry-marker">
          <span class="marker-year">2023</span>
          <div class="marker-dot"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="entry-card">
          <div class="card-header header-purple">
            <div class="header-icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M12 2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2c0 .74-.4 1.39-1 1.73V7h1a7 7 0 0 1 7 7h1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v3a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-1H2a1 1 0 0 1-1-1v-3a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h1a7 7 0 0 1 7-7h1V5.73c-.6-.34-1-.99-1-1.73a2 2 0 0 1 2-2"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="gen-badge">The AI Inflection</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>The AI Explosion</h3>
            <div class="event-list">
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot purple"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>ChatGPT & Generative AI</strong>
                  <p>AI goes mainstream. The cost of creating convincing content drops to near zero.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot green"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>Twitter Becomes X</strong>
                  <p>Continued retreat from traditional content moderation. Community Notes as the new model.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot orange"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>Israel-Hamas Information War</strong>
                  <p>Parallel information realities form instantly. Different communities see entirely different "facts."</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2024 -->
      <div class="timeline-entry" data-year="2024">
        <div class="entry-marker">
          <span class="marker-year">2024</span>
          <div class="marker-dot"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="entry-card">
          <div class="card-header header-orange">
            <div class="header-icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/>
                <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/>
                <line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/>
                <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="gen-badge">The Stress Test</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>The Global Election Year</h3>
            <div class="event-list">
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot blue"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>50+ Countries Vote</strong>
                  <p>US, EU, India, and dozens more. The biggest test of information integrity in history.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot purple"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>DSA Enforcement Begins</strong>
                  <p>Europe's Digital Services Act goes into full effect. New obligations for platforms.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot green"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>Deepfake Explosion</strong>
                  <p>Synthetic media becomes indistinguishable from reality. Audio, video, images  - all fakeable.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2025 -->
      <div class="timeline-entry timeline-entry-highlight" data-year="2025" data-gen="6">
        <div class="entry-marker">
          <span class="marker-year">2025</span>
          <div class="marker-dot"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="entry-card">
          <div class="card-header header-dark">
            <div class="header-icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                <path d="M12 16v-4M12 8h.01"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="gen-badge gen-badge-gold">GEN 6 Emerges</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>No One Is Coming</h3>
            <div class="event-list">
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot gold"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>Meta Drops Fact-Checking</strong>
                  <p>The largest platform abandons third-party verification. Community Notes becomes the only model.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot gold"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>Government Disinformation</strong>
                  <p>Official channels spread contested claims. Fact-checkers labeled as enemies. The state is no longer the anchor.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="event-item">
                <span class="event-dot gold"></span>
                <div class="event-info">
                  <strong>Platform Exodus</strong>
                  <p>Users scatter across platforms. No single town square. Fragmented information ecosystems.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="intervention-response intervention-response-dark">
              <div class="response-label">The New Paradigm</div>
              <div class="response-content">
                <strong>Collective Sensemaking</strong>
                <p>No cavalry is coming. Communities must build their own capacity for distributed verification, local deliberation, and shared coordination.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="timeline-conclusion">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="conclusion-content">
          <span class="conclusion-mantra">Disinformation adapts. Consequences evolve. Paradigms shift.</span>
          <h3>The question is no longer "who has the answers?"</h3>
          <p>It's "how do we build the capacity to navigate uncertainty together?"</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">The Challenge</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">The Problem with Interventions</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-grid">
        <div class="flip-card">
          <div class="flip-card-inner">
            <div class="flip-card-front">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                <path d="M12 16v-4M12 8h.01"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="flip-label">Exceptions, Not Examples</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-card-back">
              <h3>Gullible individuals do exist; they are exceptions not examples</h3>
              <p>Most people aren't fooled by obvious disinformation. The challenge is more nuanced.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flip-card">
          <div class="flip-card-inner">
            <div class="flip-card-front">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="flip-label">No Identical Patterns</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-card-back">
              <h3>There are no identical patterns</h3>
              <p>No disinformation campaign is created equal. Campaigns differ over time, spatially, and tactically.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flip-card">
          <div class="flip-card-inner">
            <div class="flip-card-front">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/>
                <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="flip-label">No Silver Bullets</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-card-back">
              <h3>There are no silver bullets</h3>
              <p>No single intervention works for all contexts. The dynamic context is crucially important.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Generations Section -->
  <section class="section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">The Model</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Six Generations of Interventions</h2>
        <p class="section-description">From information campaigns to collective sensemaking</p>
      </div>

      <div class="gen-timeline">
        <div class="gen-card">
          <div class="gen-number">1</div>
          <div class="gen-content">
            <div class="gen-meta">
              <span class="gen-year">Since 2014</span>
              <h3>Strategic Communication</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="gen-details">
              <div class="gen-detail">
                <span class="detail-label">Problem</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Foreign interference</span>
              </div>
              <div class="gen-detail">
                <span class="detail-label">Deficit Model</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Communication</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="gen-description">Crimea shocked the West into awareness. If adversaries spread propaganda, counter with truth. If citizens are confused, inform them.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="gen-card">
          <div class="gen-number">2</div>
          <div class="gen-content">
            <div class="gen-meta">
              <span class="gen-year">Since 2016</span>
              <h3>Debunking</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="gen-details">
              <div class="gen-detail">
                <span class="detail-label">Problem</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Truth decay</span>
              </div>
              <div class="gen-detail">
                <span class="detail-label">Deficit Model</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Verified information</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="gen-description">The 2016 elections revealed viral misinformation. If false claims were spreading, verify them, label them, and trust people will update their beliefs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="gen-card">
          <div class="gen-number">3</div>
          <div class="gen-content">
            <div class="gen-meta">
              <span class="gen-year">Since 2018</span>
              <h3>Prebunking</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="gen-details">
              <div class="gen-detail">
                <span class="detail-label">Problem</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Manipulation of domestic vulnerabilities</span>
              </div>
              <div class="gen-detail">
                <span class="detail-label">Deficit Model</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Rationality</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="gen-description">By letting potential receivers experience how disinformation is created and spread, they are getting inoculated.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="gen-card">
          <div class="gen-number">4</div>
          <div class="gen-content">
            <div class="gen-meta">
              <span class="gen-year">Since 2020</span>
              <h3>Moderation</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="gen-details">
              <div class="gen-detail">
                <span class="detail-label">Problem</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Internal actors & health risks</span>
              </div>
              <div class="gen-detail">
                <span class="detail-label">Deficit Model</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Gatekeeping</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="gen-description">COVID + political violence demanded action. Deplatform, derank, demonetize. Few producers: obstruct them, problem shrinks.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="gen-card">
          <div class="gen-number">5</div>
          <div class="gen-content">
            <div class="gen-meta">
              <span class="gen-year">Since 2022</span>
              <h3>Interaction</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="gen-details">
              <div class="gen-detail">
                <span class="detail-label">Problem</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Societal alienation</span>
              </div>
              <div class="gen-detail">
                <span class="detail-label">Deficit Model</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Social interactions</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="gen-description">Disinfo thrives in alienated, left-behind communities. People change minds through interaction, not broadcasts. Create safety, autonomy, belonging.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="gen-card gen-card-highlight">
